135
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:01,310
He stays in the room next to mine
and has a lisp.

136
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:04,510
Pleased to meet you.
I'm staying in room 101.

137
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:08,714
I'm on the same floor. I'm 186.

138
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:11,010
- Would you like to join us?
- Why not?

139
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:32,070
One of these days, it's gonna be me
