and that we're going to be turned
into dogs or canaries or something.

999
01:31:47,390 --> 01:31:49,180
I think the first thing I'm going to do

1000
01:31:49,230 --> 01:31:51,971
when I get into the city
is buy a bathrobe.

1001
01:31:52,114 --> 01:31:56,560
And then we'll go to a pool with a
high diving board, perfect for diving.

1002
01:31:56,610 --> 01:31:59,240
"And we'll do
lots of different things together,

1003
01:31:59,290 --> 01:32:01,057
serious things, not silly ones,

1004
01:32:01,114 --> 01:32:05,171
like go for walks in the park
or play the guitar together."

1005
01:32:05,857 --> 01:32:10,971
