on the back, but I don't think it's important.
-Read the notes.

1006
01:32:13,150 --> 01:32:17,114
"Portofino. Italian fishing village
and upmarket resort,

1007
01:32:17,142 --> 01:32:19,371
famous for its picturesque harbour.

1008
01:32:19,828 --> 01:32:21,971
Population: 439.

1009
01:32:22,457 --> 01:32:23,920
Beaches nearby:

1010
01:32:24,200 --> 01:32:28,542
Paraggi Beach, Camogli,
